title: I Became a Renowned Family’s Sword Prodigy
summary: I Became a Renowned Family’s Sword Prodigy ManhwaBaek Woojin is the youngest son of a renowned swordsman family who has neither talent in swordsmanship nor an impressive Aura, despite trying harder than anyone. Although he was dishonored by his own family and killed, he reincarnates as the owner of a Magic Sword. His only goal is the destruction of his own family. 위대한 가문의 검술 천재가 되었다
